  <brief_title>Extravascular Lung Water Index in Severe Sepsis</brief_title>
  <acronym>EVLI in sepsis</acronym>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Chang Gung Memorial Hospital</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Chang Gung Memorial Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate whether extravascular lung water index (EVLI) is an independent predictor for
      multiorgan dysfunction syndrome (MODS) in patients with severe sepsis and to determine if
      increased EVLI may serve as an predictor for MODS and mortality in those patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
