  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All enrolled patients were recruited consecutively on the day of MICU admission and
             within 24 hours of the diagnosis of severe sepsis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy,

          -  Age less than 18 years old, and

          -  Uncontrolled malignancy.
      </textblock>
